text: Al Rai or Alrai () may refer to: * Al Rai (Kuwaiti newspaper), a Kuwaiti newspaper * Al Ra'i (Jordanian newspaper), a Jordanian newspaper * Erraï, defunct Tunisian weekly newspaper (1977–1987) Transliterated from , it may also refer to: * Alrai, traditional Arabic name of Gamma Cephei, a binary star system in the Cepheus constellation * al-Rai, Syria, a town in Aleppo Governorate, northern Syria
title: Al Rai
